\mathbb{Z}[t] \otimes_{\mathbb{Z}} \mathbb{Z}[t] \cong \mathbb{Z}[x, y]
t \otimes 1 \mapsto x
1 \otimes t \mapsto y
\alpha : \mathbb{Z}[t] \to \mathbb{Z}[x, y]
